item.title: About
item.description: Hey there! I’m Sidath Munasinghe, and I’m excited to welcome you to my personal blog. In this space, I want to give you a little glimpse into my tech journey, my passions, and what you can expect from this blog. Who Am I? I’m a Technical Lead currently making waves at 99x, a company known for its innovation in the tech world. Before this, I had the privilege of working at Sysco Labs, where I truly began to find my footing in the fast-paced tech industry.
